can close the case now.

61
00:02:36,540 --> 00:02:38,130
I wish I could.

62
00:02:39,270 --> 00:02:41,430
But my hunch keeps telling me

63
00:02:41,560 --> 00:02:44,160
that Chen Zhao's death
isn't as simple as it appears.

64
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,490
What makes you say that?

65
00:02:45,890 --> 00:02:47,000
When Mrs. Chen came

66
00:02:47,030 --> 00:02:48,930
to claimed Chen Zhao's body,

67
00:02:49,450 --> 00:02:52,110
the expression on her face
was rather peculiar.

68
00:02:52,880 --> 00:02:54,070
Lord Shen,

69
00:02:54,420 --> 00:02:55,280
I'm here

70
00:02:55,300 --> 00:02:57,620
to claim my husband's body.

71
00:02:58,110 --> 00:02:59,000
Mao.

72
