of Chen Zhao's death.

82
00:03:43,720 --> 00:03:45,630
Now that you're suspicious,
just conduct an investigation.

83
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:46,700
Why did you ask us to come?

84
00:03:46,700 --> 00:03:48,190
I didn't ask for you.

85
00:03:48,600 --> 00:03:50,120
The one I asked for was Yu.

86
00:03:51,440 --> 00:03:52,440
Yu,

87
00:03:52,550 --> 00:03:55,200
would you join me
in visiting the Chen Mansion at night?

88
00:03:55,200 --> 00:03:55,860
