153
00:07:09,880 --> 00:07:11,060
It was up to her to decide

154
00:07:11,060 --> 00:07:12,990
whether to assist Lord Shen or not.

155
00:07:13,210 --> 00:07:15,470
Why did you try to make decisions for her?

156
00:07:16,220 --> 00:07:17,480
Why couldn't I do that?

157
00:07:17,490 --> 00:07:19,400
She's now working for the Imperial Guard,
isn't she?

158
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,310
That's true.

159
00:07:20,490 --> 00:07:22,120
But you don't own her.

160
00:07:22,140 --> 00:07:24,240
You can't stop her from making money,
can you?

161
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,520
When it comes to winning a girl's heart,

162
00:07:26,540 --> 00:07:28,370
Lord Shen does outperform you.

163
00:07:28,450 --> 00:07:30,490
You should really learn from him.

164
00:07:32,360 --> 00:07:33,820
Are you hearing yourself?

165
00:07:34,330 --> 00:07:35,890
You'll pay for this meal.

166
00:07:37,170 --> 00:07:37,970
